::Hot Rod::

He saw Feline run to him, but he didn't answer. He was watching Angel
Prime, making sure he understood. Finally they left.

Then Feline got all pissed, and ran off.
'Damn!' he thought. The only reason he was going to remain under cover
in the Alliance was her.
"Magnus, we'll have to talk later. Vehical mode!"
He transformed and went after her.

"Feline, please stop! Let's talk, I'll explain. Just please stop for
sec!"
He stayed after her.

OOC: Is Feline in Beast or Bot mode?

::DrillBit::

He heard KitKat.
"Hmm. Never a break," he replyed, more jokeing then serious.
He made his way out of the base, and headed for the pod.
